---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="Cyber Security Professional | Penetration Tester | Red Teamer"
	pubDate={new Date()}
>
	<div class="about">

		<section>
			<h2 class="section-title" id="about-me">About Me</h2>
			<div class="content">
				<p>
					I am a Cyber Security Professional with 6 years of deep interest in the field,
					including 3 years of hands-on professional experience in penetration testing
					and red teaming.
				</p>
				<p>
					My expertise includes identifying security weaknesses across web, mobile,
					API, server, and network environments, helping organizations
					improve their security posture through structured and ethical attack simulations.
				</p>
				<p>
					I hold OSCP+, OSCP, CEH Master, and eWPTXv2 certifications,
					validating advanced offensive security and red teaming capabilities.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2 class="section-title" id="skills">Skills</h2>
			<div class="content">
				<p>
					Python Programming (other languages are weak but strong in logic analysis), Web/Mobile/API/Server/Network Penetration Testing,
					Red Teaming, Source Code Analysis.
				</p>
				<p>
					Strong analytical thinking, problem solving, and collaborative teamwork
					in high-pressure security environments.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2 class="section-title" id="experience">Professional Experience</h2>
			<div class="content">
				<p><strong>PT [REDACTED] (Jakarta)</strong><br/>
				Security Consultant (August 2022 – Present)</p>

				<ul>
					<li>Performed penetration testing on web, mobile, API, server, and network environments.</li>
					<li>Conducted red teaming and phishing simulations.</li>
					<li>Delivered vulnerability assessments mapped to CVSS & OWASP.</li>
					<li>Produced detailed security reports with PoC and best practice remediation guidance.</li>
					<li>Provided security consulting for technical & non-technical stakeholders.</li>
				</ul>

				<p><strong>Amikom University Yogyakarta</strong><br/>
				Practicum Assistant (August 2021 – July 2022)</p>

				<ul>
					<li>Taught Operating Systems, Network Defense System, and Digital Forensics.</li>
					<li>Improved mastery of tools such as Volatility, SIEM platforms, and pentesting tools.</li>
					<li>Led learning sessions when lecturers were unavailable.</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2 class="section-title" id="education">Education</h2>
			<div class="content">
				<p><strong>Amikom University Yogyakarta (2019 – 2023)</strong><br/>
				Computer Engineering – Concentration in Cyber Security</p>

				<p><strong>SMK Negeri 1 Amuntai (2016 – 2019)</strong><br/>
				Computer Network Engineering</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2 class="section-title" id="certifications">Certifications</h2>
			<div class="content">
				<ul>
					<li>
						OffSec Certified Professional Plus (OSCP+)
						<p>Certificate or Evidence: <a href="https://credentials.offsec.com/c96cc9c1-78fc-42ca-af2e-bacd9eb28ae2#acc.SJ9hoQgD" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Here</a></p>
					</li>
					<li>
						OffSec Certified Professional (OSCP)
						<p>Certificate or Evidence: <a href="https://credentials.offsec.com/ef125c40-7198-4b2c-8883-b3a33df0325e" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Here</a></p>
					</li>
					<li>
						Web Application Penetration Tester eXtreme (eWPTXv2)
						<p>Certificate or Evidence: <a href="https://certs.ine.com/dcacdaa5-1c43-456d-a1b3-499e464a1139" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Here</a></p>
					</li>
					<li>
						Certified Ethical Hacker (CEH) Master
						<p>Certificate or Evidence: <a href="https://aspen.eccouncil.org/VerifyBadge?type=certification&a=CUdr915LE6ops0gskTliFye+1nUWFwtluJMZSeYu31Y=" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Here</a></p>
					</li>
					<li>
						Certified Ethical Hacker (CEH)
						<p>Certificate or Evidence: <a href="https://aspen.eccouncil.org/VerifyBadge?type=certification&a=N7dMMAdjmZojsD6ka9zmWKy1gMYK2vEJdjPORMPudeA=" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Here</a></p>
					</li>
					<li>
						Certified Ethical Hacker (CEH) Practical
						<p>Certificate or Evidence: <a href="https://aspen.eccouncil.org/VerifyBadge?type=certification&a=mA9V7kXDGee8e2pbCuEDyOg0rxOsSBDYVZwecpvf90Y=" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Here</a></p>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2 class="section-title" id="awards">Awards & Competitions</h2>
			<div class="content">
				<ul>
					<li>8th Place Patchstack S02E03 WordCamp Europe 2025 - Individual as Banua</li>
					<li>10th Place ApoorvCTF International 2025 – Team Hazaza</li>
					<li>13th Place ACECTF 1.0 International 2025 – Team Hazaza</li>
					<li>4th Place Protergo CTF 2024 – Individual as Banua</li>
					<li>Best Writeup Cryptography UIUCTF 2023 - Team TCP1P</li>
					<li>Finalist Cyber Jawara National 2022 - Team Pengen Solved Soal PWN</li>
					<li>1st Place Cyber Security PekanIT 2022 - Team Average Osint Enjoyers</li>
					<li>Top 10 Finalist Healthkathon BPJS 2022 - Team Urang Banua</li>
					<li>Finalist GEMASTIK XV & XIV Cyber Security Division - Universitas Amikom Yogyakarta</li>
					<li>2nd Place Cyber Security DOIT 5.0 2021 - Team Average Osint Enjoyers</li>
					<li>2nd Place ASEAN Skill Competition IT NSA 2019 South Kalimantan - Individual</li>
					<li>Many More Multiple National CTF Finalist</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>

	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.8rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	section {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
		gap: 1rem;
		align-items: start;
		padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(var(--border), 0.5);
	}

	.section-title {
		margin: 0;
		font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: 0.14em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: var(--accent);
		scroll-margin-top: 120px;
	}

	.content {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: rgb(var(--text-primary));
		max-width: 70ch;
	}

	.content ul {
		margin: 0.5rem 0 0 1.2rem;
	}

	.content li {
		margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		section {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>